T1  - Linking family-to-business enrichment and support to entrepreneurial success: Do female and male entrepreneurs experience different outcomes?
AU  - Powell, Gary N.
AU  - Eddleston, Kimberly A.
JO  - Journal of Business Venturing
VL  - 28
IS  - 2
SP  - 261
EP  - 280
PY  - 2013
